    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You can classify and search documents by tag set in Frontmatter. All tags you set can be viewed and searched in &lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;https://siteUrl/tags&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;5. Series&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span
      class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-wrapper&quot;
